ygData.subject: Re: cant log on
ygData.msgSnippet: EQ Updating timing has change. Last nite, Thurday around 10 pm(singapore) is the update time. Existing players were told about server shutting down in 30mins.
ygData.messageBody:
EQ Updating timing has change. Last nite, Thurday around 10 pm(singapore) is
the update time. Existing players were told about server shutting down in
30mins. If u tried to log-in during those hr u cant. that's y u cant
connect.

We are now at a "disadvanage" , as most of us play beyond the 10pm hrs. Then
again, the update is not everyday.

Yiyang Of Innorruk
